<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><u><strong>Checker:</strong></u><span=
>&nbsp;</span>As per the Checker request, the DSR API will return the list =
of Service Requests awaiting approval from the logged in Checker. The Exp A=
PI will loop through the DSR API response to deserialise the Json string pa=
yload into the respective model object(refer to the code block below for re=
ference)&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><u><strong>Note:</strong></u><span=
>&nbsp;</span>Attributes "type", "subType", "status" &amp; "dateRange" in t=
he request body are optional attributes to help filter &amp; narrow down th=
e Service Requests search</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><u><strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Exp API Response proces=
sing</span></strong></u></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">The Exp API will loop through the =
DSR API response(service Request lists) and deserialise the API Json string=
 to the respective object</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
