 action button on the UI</span></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p><=
p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(163,21,21);">Refer =
to the "Processing Condition/Logic" column for mapping details/logic</span>=
</p></td>
