llowing response</span></strong></u></p>
<ul>
<li>If all authorisation received(approved at all levels) <code class=3D"sq=
l color1" style=3D"text-align: left;">and</code><span style=3D"color: rgb(5=
1,51,51);"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><code class=3D"sql plain" style=3D"tex=
t-align: left;">the underlying target API(Payments/Bene Exp API) call<span>=
&nbsp;</span></code><code class=3D"sql keyword" style=3D"text-align: left;"=
>is</code><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><=
code class=3D"sql plain" style=3D"text-align: left;">successful</code>
<ul>
<li>Status code: 200=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
