: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
  "data": {
    "approvalWorkflowConsent": [
      {
        "code": 8120,
        "message": "Authorisation Completed",
        "details": "Exp API success response returned as json string"
      }
    ]
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(163,21,21);">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul>
<li>If authorisation required from next level of authorisers=20
<ul>
<li>Status code: 401=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
