ht">{
    "result": {
        "errors": [
            {
                "code": 8125,
                "message": "Authoriser Approval Required",
                "details": "The request is pending approval &lt;workflowId&=
gt;"
            }
        ]
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>After all authorisations received, if payment failed when submitted for=
 processing=20
<ul>
<li>Status code: 4XX/5XX or 403(entitlements lost midway) or 500=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
